#

Baked Macaroni and Cheese with a Crispy Panko Topping

45 min
$10
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodQuickEasy

Description

Creamy macaroni and cheese topped with a crunchy panko crust, perfect comfort food!

Ingredients

  • elbow macaroni: 2 cups
  • cheddar cheese: 2 cups, shredded
  • milk: 2 cups
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • all-purpose flour: 1/4 cup
  • panko breadcrumbs: 1 cup
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1/2 teaspoon
